    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "小先生的恩，老婆子记到起的。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "可算寻到你了！你就是……李天狗那一脉的小先生迈？",
      "next": "n2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "sad"
      }
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（李天狗那一脉？……哦。说的我。）正是。",
      "next": "n3",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "我屋头院坝头，夜夜都有响动！鸡也不下蛋了，狗叫到大半夜——钱，老婆子拍这点了！你总要给我看哈嘛！",
      "next": "c1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「走。带老子去看。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        },
        {
          "id": "tai",
          "text": "〔抬抬价〕「这种活路……一般先生可不接哦。」",
          "next": "c_tai"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_tai": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（一咬牙）再加十文！真的不能再多了，小先生！",
      "next": "c_tai_pay",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "sad"
      }
    },
    "c_tai_pay": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "c_jie": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "哎！哎！小先生这边走嘛——",
      "next": "n4",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "这是头一个主动找上门的活路。关二狗跟着婆子出城，一路把说书先生的词在肚子里又过了一遍。",
      "next": "n_go"
    },
    "n_go": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
